OL,3,CSeventeen suspected illegal delivery
OL,4,Cdrivers arrested at caravan park
OL,6,FSeventeen people suspected of working
OL,7,Fillegally as delivery drivers have
OL,8,Fbeen arrested at a Bristol caravan
OL,9,Fpark.
OL,11,FImmigration Enforcement officers were
OL,12,Fsent to New Stadium Road, where they
OL,13,Fdetained thirteen people. They will
OL,14,Fpotentially be removed from the UK.
OL,16,FThe four others were placed on
OL,17,Fimmigration bail and will be required
OL,18,Fto report regularly to the Home Office.
