OL,3,CSeventeen suspected illegal delivery
OL,4,Cdrivers arrested at caravan park
OL,6,FThirteen of those arrested have
OL,7,Fallegedly overstayed their permitted
OL,8,Fleave, while two are suspected to have
OL,9,Fbreached their visa conditions.
OL,10,FAnother two are suspected of breaching
OL,11,Ftheir immigration bail conditions.
OL,13,FThe Home Office said delivery drivers
OL,14,Femployed by big name companies are
OL,15,Fpaid per job and not employed directly
OL,16,Fby the company, meaning they work for
OL,17,Flonger hours and often earn
OL,18,Fsignificantly less than the national
OL,19,Fminimum wage.
