OL,6,FMinister for Border Security and
OL,7,FAsylum Angela Eagle, said: "We are
OL,8,Fdetermined to clamp down both on
OL,9,Fillegal working and the exploitative
OL,10,Ftreatment of illegal workers.
OL,12,F"Those working without the correct
OL,13,Fimmigration status and worker's rights
OL,14,Fcan find themselves in unsafe and
OL,15,Finsecure conditions, facing
OL,16,Fexploitation and even modern-day
OL,17,Fslavery, often facilitated by
OL,18,Forganised criminal gangs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
