OL,6,F"We are taking action to smash the
OL,7,Fgangs by creating the new Border
OL,8,FSecurity Command, which will
OL,9,Fcoordinate the work of law enforcement
OL,10,Fand intelligence agencies to tackle
OL,11,Forganised immigration crime."
OL,13,FEddy Montgomery, Director of
OL,14,FEnforcement, Compliance & Crime at
OL,15,FImmigration Enforcement, said: "This
OL,16,Foperation sends a clear message to
OL,17,Fthose who seek to exploit the labour
OL,18,Fmarket to employ workers illegally,
OL,19,Fand those who believe they can work
OL,20,Fhere without the correct status.
