OL,6,F"The Home Office is committed to
OL,7,Fenforcing immigration law and will not
OL,8,Ftolerate any abuse.
OL,10,F"It is our priority to uphold border
OL,11,Fsecurity and to ensure the criminals
OL,12,Fwho seek to exploit it face serious
OL,13,Fconsequences."
